@CyberQuiz.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5156

### Health Check - Testa om Ollama körs
GET {{CyberQuiz.API_HostAddress}}/api/ai/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get AI Recommendations - TEST UTAN AUTENTISERING (ändra testUserId till en riktig användare från din databas)
GET {{CyberQuiz.API_HostAddress}}/api/ai/recommendations?testUserId=1e9cc9e9-d0fc-440a-be2d-bfc89c0de7fa
Accept: application/json

###

### Get AI Recommendations - Specifik kategori
GET {{CyberQuiz.API_HostAddress}}/api/ai/recommendations?testUserId=test-user-123&subCategoryId=1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get AI Recommendations - MED AUTENTISERING (när du har token)
# GET {{CyberQuiz.API_HostAddress}}/api/ai/recommendations
# Accept: application/json
# Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###
